Crocidile became friends with monkey.
Crocidile's wife was jealous of their frienship and wanted to eat the monkey.
crocodile's wife told the crocodile to invite the monkey for lunch.
actual plan of crocodile was to kill the monkey and to eat his heart.
Next day,crocodile ivited the monkey and the monkey also agreed to join.
while monkey and crocodile began their journey,crocodile told the truth to the monkey that his wife is going to kill him.
Suddenly the wise monkey told the crocodile that he left the heart in the tree and want to pick that.
the crocodile went back to the monkey's tree and monkey escaped from the crocodile.


"Morals: intelligence wins over might"